---
import carrot from "@icons/carrot.svg";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import PrimaryButton from "../common/Primary_Button.astro";
import messageIcon from "@icons/message-tick.svg";
---

<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Window Cleaning FAQ</h2>
        <div class="faq">
            <details>
                <span
                    >Pricing depends on the size of your home or business and
                    the number of windows. We offer free quotes with no hidden
                    costs, just honest, upfront pricing for every job.</span
                >
                <summary
                    >How much does window cleaning cost in Mangerton or
                    Wollongong? <Image src={carrot} alt="dropdown" /></summary
                >
            </details>

            <details>
                <span
                    >Yes! We clean everything from suburban homes to large
                    commercial buildings. Whether you’re a homeowner or business
                    owner, we’ve got the equipment and experience to make your
                    windows spotless.</span
                >
                <summary
                    >Do you offer residential and commercial window cleaning? <Image
                        src={carrot}
                        alt="dropdown"
                    /></summary
                >
            </details>

            <details>
                <span
                    >For most homes, we recommend every 3–6 months. In coastal
                    areas like Mangerton and Wollongong, salt and dust can build
                    up faster, so quarterly cleaning keeps windows looking their
                    best.</span
                >
                <summary
                    >How often should I get my windows cleaned? <Image
                        src={carrot}
                        alt="dropdown"
                    /></summary
                >
            </details>

            <details>
                <span
                    >Yes. We’re fully insured and take all safety precautions
                    seriously, so you can have total peace of mind.</span
                >
                <summary
                    >Are you fully insured? <Image
                        src={carrot}
                        alt="dropdown"
                    /></summary
                >
            </details>

            <details>
                <span
                    >Absolutely. We offer non-abrasive solar panel cleaning to
                    help your panels work more efficiently and last longer.</span
                >
                <summary
                    >Do you clean solar panels too? <Image
                        src={carrot}
                        alt="dropdown"
                    /></summary
                >
            </details>

            <details>
                <span
                    >You can request a free quote via our website, or give us a
                    quick call during business hours (7AM–7PM). We make it easy
                    to book the way that suits you best.</span
                >
                <summary
                    >Can I book online or over the phone? <Image
                        src={carrot}
                        alt="dropdown"
                    /></summary
                >
            </details>
        </div>

        <div class="cta">
            <p>
                Have any other questions? Reach out and speak to a Window
                Cleaning expert today!
            </p>
            <PrimaryButton
                text="Get a Quote Now"
                icon={messageIcon}
                link="contact/#contact-form"
            />
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    section {
        background-color: var(--light-blue);
    }
    details {
        background-color: white;
        padding: 1rem;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--brand-blue);
        line-height: 2rem;
    }
    summary {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        font-family: "heading";
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        line-height: 1.6rem;
    }
    details[open] summary {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    details[open] summary img {
        transform: rotate(180deg);
    }
    .cta {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }
</style>
